<li>1971 <i><a href="" title="The Devils (film)">The Devils</a></i> (<a href="" title="Ken Russell">Ken Russell</a>) adapted Huxley&#39;s <i><a href="" title="The Devils of Loudun">The Devils of Loudun</a></i>.</li>
